You need:

* Linux.
  Probably.
  This code has not been tested at all under other OSes,
  *especially* not M$ Windows.
* Python >= 2.5. (Bot yet tested with 3.x.)
* Twisted.
* At least one of 1wire, LIRC, FS20, …
  … or the ability to integrate your own peripheral.
  (If so, please contribute your enhancements!)
* Some willingness to work with textual configuration files.
* Some idea of what you're actually trying to accomplish.
